{"tid":1941404,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"安倍確認東京奧運/殘奧將延期一年的提議","createTime":"2020-03-24T11:43:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T20:50:18.000Z","uid":153318,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"8bb660551a5e56f6d118b7220f909b1bc7926115","tid":1941404,"uid":153318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T11:43:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www3.nhk.or.jp/news/html/20200324/k10012348021000.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww3.nhk.or.jp%2Fnews%2Fhtml%2F20200324%2Fk10012348021000.html&d=Afoh3Yf6cz19ESyehd0SJwwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=8f17eb5d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www3.nhk.or.jp/news/html/20200324/k10012348021000.html</a><br />\n<br />\n安倍首相在與IOC會長的電話會議上，確認東京奧運/殘奧將延期一年的提議。<br />\n<br />\n安倍首相 東京五輪・パラ １年程度の延期提案へ ＩＯＣ会長に"},{"pid":"77cff74b73a553243307c886eb9f3f7671b960b8","tid":1941404,"uid":12628,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T11:44:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tt1xbvD.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftt1xbvD.gif&h=85f37404&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8c1dba08e105e1e9186eb59c908d5c024eb27837","tid":1941404,"uid":17641,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T11:45:34.000Z","msg":"2016年會係最後一屆奧運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bfd48e3029e952172c06a5bcfc80e48f9e09fce","tid":1941404,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T11:46:34.000Z","msg":"東京オリンピック・パラリンピックをめぐり、安倍総理大臣は、ＩＯＣ＝国際オリンピック委員会のバッハ会長との電話会談で、選手の準備期間などを考慮して、１年程度の延期を提案する方針を固めました。<br />\n<br />\n安倍総理大臣は、24日夜８時ごろから、総理大臣公邸でＩＯＣのバッハ会長と電話会談を行っていて、大会組織委員会の森会長や東京都の小池知事、橋本担当大臣らも同席しています。<br />\n<br />\nこれに先立って、安倍総理大臣は、ＩＯＣが東京オリンピック・パラリンピックを延期する検討を始めたことを踏まえ、選手の準備期間などを考慮して、１年程度の延期を提案する方針を固めました。<br />\n<br />\n会談で、安倍総理大臣は、今回のＩＯＣの判断は、完全な形で大会を実施するという日本の方針に沿うものだとして謝意を伝えることにしています。<br />\n<br />\nその上で、１年程度の延期をバッハ会長に提案するとともに、延期する場合の日程を含め、できるだけ早く対応を決定するよう要請するものとみられます。"},{"pid":"520b8dca6b9a59117d741695615679ecf4a67664","tid":1941404,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T11:47:19.000Z","msg":"早知今日  何必當初 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7562b256a3c461ab83a473e7420b9c52589dbe1d","tid":1941404,"uid":243380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"77cff74b73a553243307c886eb9f3f7671b960b8","tid":1941404,"uid":12628,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T11:44:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tt1xbvD.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftt1xbvD.gif&h=85f37404&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T11:50:02.000Z","msg":"幾多年冇睇過呢張gif<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc9b31b41564d0f4bb37af2c3e657574c8e78179","tid":1941404,"uid":31098,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T11:51:07.000Z","msg":"算啦，遲決定改期都好過夾硬嚟<br />\n夾硬嚟爆發大感染，日本人嘅 reputation 就一鋪清袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都係嗰句，出年疫情過咗嘅話，我到時去東京瘋狂食買玩睇比賽喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"766992d6cf385c35f8a292a3443416c3a6e3eadb","tid":1941404,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c1dba08e105e1e9186eb59c908d5c024eb27837","tid":1941404,"uid":17641,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T11:45:34.000Z","msg":"2016年會係最後一屆奧運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T11:51:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore